00:50:02.120 --> 00:50:05.870 align:middle line:84%
It's morning time, and I have
made myself some breakfast.

00:50:05.870 --> 00:50:15.320 align:middle line:84%
And I have natto,
soybean, and pickles.

00:50:15.320 --> 00:50:17.960 align:middle line:84%
