00:53:33.860 --> 00:53:38.240 align:middle line:84%
The major difference seems to
be the quantity that they eat.

00:53:38.240 --> 00:53:39.860 align:middle line:84%
>> This is the
normal, what we call,

00:53:39.860 --> 00:53:41.420 align:middle line:90%
[SPEAKING JAPANESE] in Japan.

