00:53:54.280 --> 00:53:54.910 align:middle line:90%
>> Everybody.

00:53:54.910 --> 00:53:55.200 align:middle line:90%
Everybody.

00:53:55.200 --> 00:53:55.490 align:middle line:90%
>> Everyone.

00:53:55.490 --> 00:53:55.760 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:53:55.760 --> 00:53:56.120 align:middle line:90%
>> everybody.

00:53:56.120 --> 00:53:57.980 align:middle line:84%
>> But the young ones
