00:53:57.980 --> 00:53:58.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, yeah.

00:53:58.780 --> 00:53:59.580 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:53:59.580 --> 00:54:00.810 align:middle line:90%
This is the difference, yeah?

00:54:00.810 --> 00:54:01.610 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, right.

00:54:01.610 --> 00:54:04.970 align:middle line:84%
