you're going to find out,

00:54:12.230 --> 00:54:13.897 align:middle line:84%
because they, all of
them, catch trains.

00:54:13.897 --> 00:54:16.270 align:middle line:90%


00:54:16.270 --> 00:54:19.230 align:middle line:84%
>> My meeting with Konishiki
gave me a lot to think about.

00:54:19.230 --> 00:54:22.010 align:middle line:84%
While Japanese food is
healthy for the most part,

00:54:22.010 --> 00:54:24.650 align:middle line:84%
overeating can still
cause problems.

00:54:24.650 --> 00:54:28.130 align:middle line:84%
And Konishiki reinforced just
how much the Japanese walk.

00:54:28.130 --> 00:54:31.670 align:middle line:84%
They walk to work, to
school, to the grocery store.

00:54:31.670 --> 00:54:34.130 align:middle line:90%
They walk everywhere.

00:54:34.130 --> 00:54:37.610 align:middle line:84%
