average about 12,000 steps.

00:54:41.510 --> 00:54:43.700 align:middle line:84%
And my day with
Kazu the businessmen

00:54:43.700 --> 00:54:47.090 align:middle line:84%
saw this number
jump to over 20,000.

00:54:47.090 --> 00:54:50.030 align:middle line:84%
This daily exercise is
more vital to the lifestyle

00:54:50.030 --> 00:54:52.370 align:middle line:90%
than I initially thought.

00:54:52.370 --> 00:54:54.590 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to need to keep
it up when I get home

00:54:54.590 --> 00:54:57.990 align:middle line:90%
if I want to maintain the diet.

00:54:57.990 --> 00:55:01.070 align:middle line:84%
Konishiki also reminded me
something my dietician told me

00:55:01.070 --> 00:55:02.780 align:middle line:90%
about portion sizes.

00:55:02.780 --> 00:55:05.330 align:middle line:84%
She told me not to eat more
than the size of my fist

00:55:05.330 --> 00:55:08.270 align:middle line:90%
during any given meal.

00:55:08.270 --> 00:55:10.160 align:middle line:84%
I realized that
the Japanese custom

00:55:10.160 --> 00:55:12.860 align:middle line:84%
