on backwards or something?

00:55:56.110 --> 00:55:56.910 align:middle line:90%
>> That's OK.

00:55:56.910 --> 00:55:57.330 align:middle line:90%
>> It's OK?

00:55:57.330 --> 00:55:57.770 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:55:57.770 --> 00:55:58.770 align:middle line:90%
