without cutting it?

00:56:56.890 --> 00:56:57.910 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:56:57.910 --> 00:57:00.120 align:middle line:90%
>> I do that?

00:57:00.120 --> 00:57:00.920 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, please.

00:57:00.920 --> 00:57:06.050 align:middle line:90%


00:57:06.050 --> 00:57:07.270 align:middle line:90%
>> And you pull it apart.

00:57:07.270 --> 00:57:08.590 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:57:08.590 --> 00:57:09.390 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:57:09.390 --> 00:57:14.395 align:middle line:90%


00:57:14.395 --> 00:57:15.800 align:middle line:90%
>> It is difficult for me.

00:57:15.800 --> 00:57:19.810 align:middle line:90%


00:57:19.810 --> 00:57:20.610 align:middle line:90%
>> By chopsticks.

00:57:20.610 --> 00:57:21.410 align:middle line:90%
Amazing.

00:57:21.410 --> 00:57:22.590 align:middle line:90%
Thank you so much.

00:57:22.590 --> 00:57:23.800 align:middle line:90%
You're like my dad now.

00:57:23.800 --> 00:57:24.600 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yes?

00:57:24.600 --> 00:57:26.225 align:middle line:84%
>> You cut my food
for me before I eat.

