Is that OK?

00:57:35.515 --> 00:57:35.820 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:57:35.820 --> 00:57:36.620 align:middle line:90%
That's OK.

00:57:36.620 --> 00:57:40.020 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:57:40.020 --> 00:57:41.590 align:middle line:90%
Mm.

00:57:41.590 --> 00:57:44.310 align:middle line:84%
And slurping--
[SLURPS] --is good?

00:57:44.310 --> 00:57:50.390 align:middle line:90%


00:57:50.390 --> 00:57:53.010 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:57:53.010 --> 00:57:55.590 align:middle line:84%
>> So I shouldn't-- with meat,
so I shouldn't make a lot

00:57:55.590 --> 00:57:56.390 align:middle line:90%
of slurping?

00:57:56.390 --> 00:57:58.527 align:middle line:90%


00:57:58.527 --> 00:57:59.610 align:middle line:90%
>> A little bit, but not--

00:57:59.610 --> 00:58:00.786 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

