[SLURPS QUIETLY]

00:58:01.830 --> 00:58:02.670 align:middle line:90%
>> Good?

00:58:02.670 --> 00:58:03.240 align:middle line:90%
Not bad?

00:58:03.240 --> 00:58:04.190 align:middle line:90%
That was OK?

00:58:04.190 --> 00:58:04.550 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:58:04.550 --> 00:58:04.790 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:58:04.790 --> 00:58:05.994 align:middle line:90%
This?

00:58:05.994 --> 00:58:08.280 align:middle line:90%
[SLURPS, COUGHS]

